 :<del>Chameleon something</del><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0002HZ7VS?ie=UTF8&tag=ikunoz-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative= 7399&creativeASIN=B0002HZ7VS">Colorette</a>: A game to collect chameleons. The score increases progressively depending on the number of pieces. However, from the fourth color onward, the more chameleons you collect, the more points you lose. You don't want to take the colors you don't need, but you have to take all the cards in the pile. Look at the pile of garbage." If you are indecisive, you may end up picking up a pile of garbage you don't want, or if you are in a hurry to pick up cards because you don't want to mix in garbage, you may not get any points later on.
 
